## Selected Candidate

Selected: `DOCUMENTATION-EPIC-01 - Publication Authority and Versioning Consolidation`

Why:

- publication authority and root/global versioning are unresolved portfolio-wide controls;
- the work can remain documentation/governance-only and non-production;
- it improves provenance and ownership without opening execution-sensitive gates;
- Academy and Mining are complete non-production, ACS is paused, Marketplace is backlog-ready, and Defi requires remediation before features.

## Holds

All other nuclei remain on HOLD for this board cycle. HOLD means no next L4 consolidation sprint is selected now; it does not imply regression.

## Boundary Statement

No board decision authorizes production readiness, governance execution, treasury movement, wallet signing, trading, DEX execution, marketplace settlement, mining payouts, lottery payouts, ACS provisioning, billing execution, production credentials or on-chain writes.
